title: Texas Flip and Move S02E11 Groovy Flip vs Pool House PDTV.x264-J
description:
Texas Flip and Move - Season 2, Episode 11




Randy's Far-out Flip vs. Northwest Cabin

Randy discovers that his new house is straight out of the 1970's on the inside with a faux fireplace, vaulted beam ceiling and wall-to-wall knotty pine. Meanwhile, when the Snows get outbid at another auction, they still have an ace up their sleeves. The Sisters decide to use a pool house that had come with another house they had won.




Original Air Date: 27-Nov-2015
